(468, 9, '2017-07-10 23:43:54', '2017-07-10 23:43:54', '<ul class="Reset">\r\n 	<li class="pageli">\r\n<div id="pf1" class="page-outer-wrapper">\r\n<div class="page-inner-wrapper">\r\n<div id="pg-1pf1" class="pf pg-1w0 pg-1h0">\r\n<div class="pc pg-1pc1 pg-1w0 pg-1h0">\r\n<div class="t pg-1m0 pg-1x3 pg-1h4 pg-1y3 pg-1ff1 pg-1fs2 pg-1fc0 pg-1sc0 pg-1ls0 pg-1ws0">JOB DESCRIPTION</div>\r\n<div class="t pg-1m0 pg-1x3 pg-1h4 pg-1y4 pg-1ff1 pg-1fs2 pg-1fc0 pg-1sc0 pg-1ls0 pg-1ws0">JOB TITLE: Caregiver/MedTech</div>\r\n<div class="t pg-1m0 pg-1x3 pg-1h4 pg-1y5 pg-1ff2 pg-1fs2 pg-1fc0 pg-1sc0 pg-1ls0 pg-1ws0">Department: Health Services</div>\r\n<div class="t pg-1m0 pg-1x3 pg-1h4 pg-1y6 pg-1ff2 pg-1fs2 pg-1fc0 pg-1sc0 pg-1ls0 pg-1ws0">Supervised by: Administrator/Facility Manager</div>\r\n<div class="t pg-1m0 pg-1x3 pg-1h4 pg-1y7 pg-1ff2 pg-1fs2 pg-1fc0 pg-1sc0 pg-1ls0 pg-1ws0">Supervises: None</div>\r\n<div class="t pg-1m0 pg-1x3 pg-1h2 pg-1y8 pg-1ff1 pg-1fs0 pg-1fc0 pg-1sc0 pg-1ls0 pg-1ws0">Position Summary</div>\r\n<div class="t pg-1m0 pg-1x3 pg-1h5 pg-1y9 pg-1ff2 pg-1fs3 pg-1fc0 pg-1sc0 pg-1ls0 pg-1ws0">This position provides assistance to residents with activities of daily living as well as medication management.</div>\r\n<div class="t pg-1m0 pg-1x3 pg-1h5 pg-1ya pg-1ff2 pg-1fs3 pg-1fc0 pg-1sc0 pg-1ls0 pg-1ws0">Emergency first aid may be required from time to time. Caregivers/Med Techs will be supervised by the Assisted Living</div>\r\n<div class="t pg-1m0 pg-1x3 pg-1h5 pg-1yb pg-1ff2 pg-1fs3 pg-1fc0 pg-1sc0 pg-1ls0 pg-1ws0">Facility Manager and the Assisted Living Facility Administrator.</div>\r\n<div class="t pg-1m0 pg-1x3 pg-1h5 pg-1yc pg-1ff1 pg-1fs3 pg-1fc0 pg-1sc0 pg-1ls0 pg-1ws0">Essential Functions</div>\r\n<div class="t pg-1m0 pg-1x3 pg-1h5 pg-1yd pg-1ff2 pg-1fs3 pg-1fc0 pg-1sc0 pg-1ls0 pg-1ws0"> Administer medications following established guidelines, policies and procedures, and state law</div>\r\n<div class="t pg-1m0 pg-1x3 pg-1h5 pg-1ye pg-1ff2 pg-1fs3 pg-1fc0 pg-1sc0 pg-1ls0 pg-1ws0"> Assist residents with activities of daily living as specified in the residents service and care plan</div>\r\n<div class="t pg-1m0 pg-1x3 pg-1h5 pg-1yf pg-1ff2 pg-1fs3 pg-1fc0 pg-1sc0 pg-1ls0 pg-1ws0"> Assist residents with bathing, dressing or undressing, grooming, transferring, toileting, and escort to and from</div>\r\n<div class="t pg-1m0 pg-1x3 pg-1h5 pg-1y10 pg-1ff2 pg-1fs3 pg-1fc0 pg-1sc0 pg-1ls0 pg-1ws0">appointments and other destinations.</div>\r\n<div class="t pg-1m0 pg-1x3 pg-1h5 pg-1y11 pg-1ff2 pg-1fs3 pg-1fc0 pg-1sc0 pg-1ls0 pg-1ws0"> Responsible for documenting in resident records any significant changes in residents condition and report such changes</div>\r\n<div class="t pg-1m0 pg-1x3 pg-1h5 pg-1y12 pg-1ff2 pg-1fs3 pg-1fc0 pg-1sc0 pg-1ls0 pg-1ws0">to the Resident Services Director</div>\r\n<div class="t pg-1m0 pg-1x3 pg-1h5 pg-1y13 pg-1ff2 pg-1fs3 pg-1fc0 pg-1sc0 pg-1ls0 pg-1ws0"> Take vital signs, including respirations, temperature, blood pressure and pulse and record information appropriately</div>\r\n<div class="t pg-1m0 pg-1x3 pg-1h5 pg-1y14 pg-1ff2 pg-1fs3 pg-1fc0 pg-1sc0 pg-1ls0 pg-1ws0"> Responsible for participating in and supporting activity program</div>\r\n<div class="t pg-1m0 pg-1x3 pg-1h5 pg-1y15 pg-1ff2 pg-1fs3 pg-1fc0 pg-1sc0 pg-1ls0 pg-1ws0"> Provide companionship to residents</div>\r\n<div class="t pg-1m0 pg-1x3 pg-1h5 pg-1y16 pg-1ff2 pg-1fs3 pg-1fc0 pg-1sc0 pg-1ls0 pg-1ws0"> Monitor environment for safety or to maintain well-being of residents</div>\r\n<div class="t pg-1m0 pg-1x3 pg-1h5 pg-1y17 pg-1ff2 pg-1fs3 pg-1fc0 pg-1sc0 pg-1ls0 pg-1ws0"> Report incidents to the Resident Services Director and/or Assisted Living Director using the appropriate forms</div>\r\n<div class="t pg-1m0 pg-1x3 pg-1h5 pg-1y18 pg-1ff2 pg-1fs3 pg-1fc0 pg-1sc0 pg-1ls0 pg-1ws0"> Occasional light housekeeping, such as bed making and changing of linens</div>\r\n<div class="t pg-1m0 pg-1x3 pg-1h5 pg-1y19 pg-1ff2 pg-1fs3 pg-1fc0 p