(645, 1, '2017-07-28 13:59:22', '2017-07-28 13:59:22', 'Seniors maintaining their independence is crucial for <a href="http://amberlakeassistedliving.com/goodsamservices/arrangement-for-transportation/"><u>healthy and active aging</u></a>. A big part of independence is transportation. At Amberlake Assisted Living we provide a door-to-door system where advance reservations are made to take an elderly individual from one place to another. These services provide comfort, convenience, and flexibility. <a href="http://amberlakeassistedliving.com/goodsamservices/arrangement-for-transportation/"><u>Fixed route or scheduled services transport for elderly</u></a> individuals between fixed stops on a route.', 'Arrangement For Transportation', '<img class="service_icon" src="/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/amberlake_service_logo2.png"><br />\r\nWe provide a door-to-door system where advance reservations are made to take an elderly individual from one place to another', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'arrangement-for-transportation', '', '', '2017-08-02 06:58:33', '2017-08-02 06:58:33', '', 0, 'http://amberlakeassistedliving.com/?post_type=goodsamservices&#038;p=645', 0, 'goodsamservices', '', 0),
